Tuna irin masifar da suka shiga a bara a sanadin ambaliyar ruwa, yasa hankalin mutane da daman a jihohin Sokoto da kebbi yake a tashe saboda tsoron abinda zai faru a bana.
Wannan fargabar ta biyo bayan hasashen da aka yi na cewa mai yiyuwa ne a sami ruwan sama a wannan shekara fiyeda da na bara.
A shekarar da ta gabata dimbin mutane sun rasa muhallansu da gonnaki a sanadin faccewar madatsar ruwa ta Goronyo wacce itace madatsa ta biyu a girma a duk fadin Afrika, Wakilin Muryar Amurka a Sokoto, Murtala Faruk Sanyinna ya zanta da wasu mazuna karamar hukumar Goronyo da suka ce suna cikin damuwa ganin har yanzu baÊ¼a warware matsalolin da suka janyo ambaliyar bara ba.
